493
00:33:13.591 --> 00:33:16.136
I can't go back to jail.
Please.

494
00:33:16.219 --> 00:33:17.553
I missed Hell's Kitchen.

495
00:33:17.637 --> 00:33:18.847
Yeah.

496
00:33:18.930 --> 00:33:21.224
It didn't miss you.

497
00:33:24.435 --> 00:33:25.436
Fine.

498
00:33:25.520 --> 00:33:27.773
Know what?
Be like that.

499
00:33:29.274 --> 00:33:32.027
'Cause we both know I'll be back out
by the end of the month...

500
00:33:36.656 --> 00:33:37.866
I'll see you then.

501
00:33:48.293 --> 00:33:49.836
Members only. pork chop.

502
00:33:49.920 --> 00:33:52.088
It's okay. I'm meeting a friend.

503
00:33:53.464 --> 00:33:54.966
Get lost or get hurt.

504
00:33:55.967 --> 00:33:59.637
He's a full-patch member
of the Dogs of Hell.

505
00:33:59.720 --> 00:34:01.347
I swear. I just need to talk to him.

506
00:34:01.431 --> 00:34:02.974
What's this big shot's name?

507
00:34:03.058 --> 00:34:04.392
Smitty.

508
00:34:06.477 --> 00:34:07.562
Don't move.

509
00:34:21.326 --> 00:34:22.618
Does it look like I'm packing?

510
00:34:22.702 --> 00:34:24.495
Gonna wish you were.

511
00:34:29.209 --> 00:34:30.710
Come with me.

512
00:34:55.026 --> 00:34:56.777
Look at this asshole.

513
00:35:07.205 --> 00:35:08.915
Says he's here to see Smitty.

514
00:35:12.710 --> 00:35:14.504
Old friend.

515
00:35:16.006 --> 00:35:17.673
- Old friend?
- Yeah.

516
00:35:17.757 --> 00:35:20.510
Third grade.
Sister Haney's class?

517
00:35:20.593 --> 00:35:22.470
She really had it in for us.

518
00:35:23.263 --> 00:35:26.099
Is he around or should I just...
Ow! No. no. no. no!

519
00:35:26.182 --> 00:35:28.018
Holy shit!

520
00:35:30.145 --> 00:35:33.273
- What's your name?
- Foggy! Franklin Nelson!

521
00:35:34.565 --> 00:35:35.566
Never heard of you.

522
00:35:35.650 --> 00:35:38.778
I've known Smitty
for a long time.

523
00:35:39.612 --> 00:35:41.114
Oh. yeah? Me. too.

524
00:35:41.197 --> 00:35:43.158
Obviously. we went on different
career paths along the way...

525
00:35:43.241 --> 00:35:45.076
- Is this funny to you?
- No.

526
00:35:45.160 --> 00:35:47.245
- No. sir.
- 'Cause I'm two seconds away

527
00:35:47.328 --> 00:35:49.998
- from slitting your throat.
- I'm not a cop. okay?

528
00:35:52.500 --> 00:35:53.709
You a fed?

529
00:35:53.793 --> 00:35:55.128
I'm a lawyer.

530
00:35:56.462 --> 00:35:59.215
Look. I just...
I just need five minutes

531
00:35:59.299 --> 00:36:02.385
with Smitty and then I swear. I'm gone.

532
00:36:02.468 --> 00:36:03.594
Yeah. you're gone now.

533
00:36:03.678 --> 00:36:07.307
Ever walk back in here again.
and you'll leave in pieces.

534
00:36:07.390 --> 00:36:09.267
Nod if you understand me.

535
00:36:14.605 --> 00:36:17.150
Take him out back.
show him how we feel about lawyers.

536
00:36:17.233 --> 00:36:18.473
No. please. no. no. no. no. no.

537
00:39:15.495 --> 00:39:17.622
It's okay.
I'm gonna get you down.

538
00:39:17.705 --> 00:39:20.750
I'm gonna get you down.
I'm gonna get you down.

539
00:39:28.716 --> 00:39:30.796
It was a mistake coming here.
I realize that.

540
00:39:30.843 --> 00:39:32.470
- Shut up!
- I just wanted to help people. I swear.

541
00:39:32.553 --> 00:39:34.930
- Smitty would understand!
- Smitty's dead. asshole.

542
00:39:35.014 --> 00:39:36.224
What?

543
00:39:37.892 --> 00:39:40.645
You have to believe me.
I... I didn't know that.

544
00:39:40.728 --> 00:39:42.021
Oh. I believe
there's a lot you don't know.

545
00:39:42.105 --> 00:39:43.314
Whoa. okay. look.

546
00:39:43.398 --> 00:39:46.234
Smitty was a long time ago.

547
00:39:46.317 --> 00:39:48.486
Couple years ago.
I helped a guy named Foster.

548
00:39:48.569 --> 00:39:50.238
- He was a biker!
- Not one of ours.

549
00:39:50.321 --> 00:39:51.781
- Ricky Wex?
- Shut up!

550
00:39:51.864 --> 00:39:53.324
I helped a guy named Pope!

551
00:39:54.409 --> 00:39:58.204
Yeah. the VA said that his injuries
weren't sustained during battle.

552
00:39:58.288 --> 00:39:59.914
but they were!

553
00:39:59.997 --> 00:40:02.792
They just didn't manifest themselves
for 20 years.

554
00:40:02.875 --> 00:40:05.795
Uh. we got his operation sorted and then.

555
00:40:05.878 --> 00:40:08.047
a couple of months later.
he was back on his Harley.

556
00:40:08.131 --> 00:40:11.217
doing whatever it is you guys do.
Which is none of my business!

557
00:40:12.552 --> 00:40:14.179
You helped Pope?

558
00:40:18.433 --> 00:40:19.600
Get the hell out of here.

559
00:40:21.477 --> 00:40:23.020
- Really?
- Now!

560
00:40:27.983 --> 00:40:29.402
What happened to Smitty?

561
00:40:32.197 --> 00:40:33.948
- You serious?
- I came here for a reason.

562
00:40:34.031 --> 00:40:35.450
I just need answers!

563
00:40:35.533 --> 00:40:39.119
Look. if I don't get answers.
a lot of innocent blood could be shed.

564
00:40:39.204 --> 00:40:42.623
People who both you and I care about
are gonna get hurt.

565
00:40:42.707 --> 00:40:44.875
And you don't seem like
the most sentimental guy.

566
00:40:44.959 --> 00:40:47.295
but you're still listening.

567
00:40:47.378 --> 00:40:52.508
And that knife isn't in my neck.
so I have to believe that right now...

568
00:40:53.759 --> 00:40:56.387
maybe you and I are on the same side.

569
00:40:57.972 --> 00:41:01.434
You got guts. Harvard.
I'll give you that.

570
00:41:02.852 --> 00:41:06.689
Columbia. actually. but it's not courage.

571
00:41:06.772 --> 00:41:08.483
It's more like sheer adrenaline.

572
00:41:10.109 --> 00:41:11.819
Hey. look. I wouldn't be asking.

573
00:41:11.902 --> 00:41:16.491
I wouldn't be here doing this
if it wasn't important.

574
00:41:27.543 --> 00:41:29.086
Smitty was on a run.

575
00:41:29.169 --> 00:41:32.298
I-90 with four brothers.
transporting a big score.

576
00:41:32.382 --> 00:41:36.594
They were hit by a goddamn army.
Their whole crew was cut to pieces.

577
00:41:36.677 --> 00:41:38.263
Left there like roadkill.

578
00:41:38.346 --> 00:41:40.473
- Any idea who did it?
- Nah.

579
00:41:40.556 --> 00:41:43.684
New crew. doesn't matter.
Whoever they are. we're gonna find 'em.

580
00:41:43.768 --> 00:41:47.104
And when we do. you wanna be
very far away from the action.

581
00:41:48.105 --> 00:41:51.108
You didn't hear none of this from me.
Now go.

582
00:41:52.818 --> 00:41:54.111
And don't come back.

583
00:42:07.500 --> 00:42:10.253
I always knew
the devil would come for me.

584
00:42:11.504 --> 00:42:13.506
But I thought I would be dead first.

585
00:42:13.589 --> 00:42:15.550
- I'm gonna get some help.
- No!

586
00:42:15.633 --> 00:42:18.052
No... no...

587
00:42:24.850 --> 00:42:26.394
Who did this?

588
00:42:27.186 --> 00:42:28.854
No one escapes this.

589
00:42:29.814 --> 00:42:32.900
No one can get away.

590
00:42:34.319 --> 00:42:35.736
Tell me.

591
00:42:43.494 --> 00:42:45.413
Tell me who they are.

592
00:42:49.709 --> 00:42:51.168
No "they."

593
00:42:51.251 --> 00:42:52.753
Him.

594
00:42:54.129 --> 00:42:55.673
It's one man.

595
00:43:22.992 --> 00:43:25.536
Hold it right there.

596
00:43:29.582 --> 00:43:32.292
Oh. my God!

597
00:43:33.836 --> 00:43:35.713
Oh. God.

598
00:43:35.796 --> 00:43:37.297
What was that?

599
00:43:37.382 --> 00:43:39.634
No. no. no. no. no. no. no.

600
00:43:39.717 --> 00:43:41.218
Shit.

601
00:43:41.301 --> 00:43:42.887
Someone's come to finish the job.

602
00:43:42.970 --> 00:43:44.639
Shh! Don't move.

603
00:43:45.556 --> 00:43:46.849
No. to hell with that.

604
00:43:53.272 --> 00:43:55.149
He's got a gun!

605
00:43:55.232 --> 00:43:57.735
Shit.

606
00:43:57.818 --> 00:44:00.029
Come on. come on. come on!

607
00:44:00.112 --> 00:44:01.822
Come on!

608
00:44:35.565 --> 00:44:38.233
Dear God.

609
00:44:38.317 --> 00:44:39.694
Shit.

610
00:44:39.777 --> 00:44:41.737
What? You...
You don't have the right keys?

611
00:44:41.821 --> 00:44:44.073
- Shut up! Shut up!
- Is this even your car?

612
00:44:44.156 --> 00:44:46.283
- Belonged to a friend.
- Where's he?

613
00:44:47.284 --> 00:44:48.619
He's dead.

614
00:44:49.829 --> 00:44:51.371
Get in!

615
00:46:47.822 --> 00:46:49.156
Bang.

616
00:46:50.305 --> 00:47:50.621
